Executive Profile
Mark D. Gersten  Chief Financial Officer and Treasurer, AB Equity Income FundAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 80 Board Members in 80 different organizations across 91 different industries.See Board Relationships67--
Background

		Mr. Mark D. Gersten served as the Chief Financial Officer and Treasurer of The Ibero-America Fund, Inc (formerly, Spain Fund, Inc.) since June 1988 and served as its Principal Accounting Officer. Mr. Gersten is an independent consultant to clients in the investment management industry. He has more than 30 years of experience in the financial services industry serving in various roles. Mr. Gersten possesses deep expertise in fund operations and third party engagements. ... He served as Principal Accounting Officer, Chief Financial Officer and Treasurer of various funds in Alliance/AllianceBernstein/AB Large/AMC fund complex. Prior to his joining AllianceBernstein, he held key industry positions at Prudential-Bache Securities and PriceWaterhouseCoopers. Prior to 2012, Mr. Gersten spent the last 26 years in various executive roles at AllianceBernstein LP, including Senior Vice President – Global Fund Administration and Treasurer and Chief Financial Officer of Mutual Funds. His Principal Occupation during the past 5 years includes Senior Vice President of Alliance Global Investor Services, Inc. (“AGIS“), and Vice President of AllianceBernstein Investment Research and Management, Inc., with which he has been associated since prior to 1999. He served as the Vice President of AFD, an affiliate of ACM Income Fund Inc. He served as the Chief Financial Officer, Principal Accounting Officer and Treasurer of AllianceBernstein L.P. and AllianceBernstein Trust. He serves as Chairman of Two Roads Shared Trust - Anfield Universal Fixed Income Fund. He serves as the Chairman of the Board at Two Roads Shared Trust - Fortunatus Protactical New Opportunity Fund. He has been Independent Trustee of Two Roads Shared Trust - Anfield Universal Fixed Income Fund since 2012. Mr. Gersten is a Certified Public Accountant and holds an MBA in accounting.Read Full Background




